\begin_layout Proof
Fix some iteration 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

.
 Let 
\begin_inset Formula $x=x^{(k)},s=s^{(k)},t=t^{(k)},x'=x^{(k+1)},s'=s^{(k+1)}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $t'=t^{(k+1)}$
\end_inset

